Enum ParameterType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ParameterType>
      • io.vertx.ext.web.api.validation.ParameterType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ParameterType>
    Deprecated. 
    You should use the new module vertx-web-openapi

    @Deprecated
public enum ParameterType
extends Enum<ParameterType>
    ParameterType contains prebuilt type validators. To access to ParameterTypeValidator of every ParameterType, use validationMethod()
    Author:
    Francesco Guardiani @slinkydeveloper
